data.journal: russian journal of genetics: applied research
data.abstracttext: this paper highlights work on the mobilization and conservation of plant genetic resources of azerbaijan. it gives a summary of the activities of the national genebank at the genetic resources institute of the national academy of sciences of azerbaijan, establishment of the information center, and development of a unified information system with a centralized database for the plant genetic resources of azerbaijan. © 2013 pleiades publishing, ltd.
